{"tid":862433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三將提出明年加消費稅至10%","createTime":"2018-10-14T23:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T00:32:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13fe28459b6068e29aab3ad4cb40cfba60484da4","tid":862433,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:15:01.000Z","msg":"安倍晉三將提出明年加消費稅至10%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1966526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1966526&d=o6wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=000627d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1966526</a><br />\n<br />\n日本共同社報道，日本首相安倍晉三將於明日在內閣會議上，宣布把消費稅率由8%增至10%，並計劃在明年10月1日生效。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，是次徵稅目的是確保財政能夠負擔各社會保障制度，加稅是無可避免，並強調政府會採取所有必要措施，減少加稅造成負面影響，但日本各界擔心加稅或引發經濟衰退。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本央行行長黑田東彥相信，上調消費稅對經濟不會產生嚴重負面影響，又指上調消費稅的影響比上一次「小得多」。"},{"pid":"7664855bce7699854f6228f91fcfe8a8d58c17a8","tid":862433,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"8176daf0ee7a133057ae6af2b002b9bb0437b96e","tid":862433,"uid":52669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"就算佢拎收多左既錢去起人工島 我都會支持"}]}